# Halyvernoxian App File Structure

## Core Files
```
lib/
├── main.dart              # App entry point
├── app.dart               # Root widget and navigation
├── theme.dart             # App theme definition
└── routes.dart            # Route definitions
```

## Feature: Love Diary
```
lib/features/love_diary/
├── screens/
│   ├── love_diary_screen.dart     # Main love diary screen
│   └── add_memory_screen.dart     # Add new memory form
├── widgets/
│   ├── love_counter.dart          # Days counter widget
│   ├── milestone_card.dart        # Milestone card widget
│   └── timeline_item.dart         # Timeline entry widget
└── models/
    ├── memory.dart                # Memory data model
    └── milestone.dart             # Milestone data model
```

